A) Project Coordination

• Assist the project teams at Bank'headquarters in identification and preparation of projects by  collecting, analyzing and providing relevant sector information to the respective colleagues at headquarters and in the country office;
• Contribute to the efficiency of the project implementation by regularly monitoring the implementation process, reporting to headquarters on project progress, identifying obstacles and contributing ideas on how to overcome them;
• Coordinate among and assist the implementing agencies such as various Cambodian ministries,as well as other local and international partners (such as consultants and contractors working on a particular project) in resolving issues arising during the whole project cycle.

